T1  - The Use of Mathematical Models in Plant Maintenance Decision Making
AU  - Turban, Efraim
Y1  - 1967/02/01
PY  - 1967
DA  - 1967/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.13.6.B342
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.13.6.B342
