T1  - Management Science in the World of Today and Tomorrow
AU  - Dantzig, George B.
Y1  - 1967/02/01
PY  - 1967
DA  - 1967/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.13.6.C107
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.13.6.C107
